<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how" style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 40px;">
  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0;">
    <div class="section-tag">How It Works</div>
    <h2>From permit filed to you on-site —<br>in three steps</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto;">No scraping, no cold lists. Just real-time permit intelligence delivered straight to your dashboard.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="how-grid">
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-step">1</div>
      <h3>Set Your Trade & Territory</h3>
      <p>Choose your trade (plumbing, electrical, GC, roofing, and more) and the boroughs or neighborhoods you work in. KonXPro filters everything else out.</p>
      <div class="connector"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-step">2</div>
      <h3>Get Real-Time Alerts</h3>
      <p>The moment NYC DOB files a permit that matches your criteria, you get an instant alert — email, SMS, or in-app push. You're always first to know.</p>
      <div class="connector"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="how-card">
      <div class="how-step">3</div>
      <h3>Contact the Owner & Win the Job</h3>
      <p>Each permit includes the property owner's contact details, filing history, and estimated job value. Reach out before your competitors even hear about it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features" style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px 80px;">
  <div>
    <div class="section-tag">Features</div>
    <h2>Everything you need to dominate<br>your local market</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built specifically for NYC trade contractors, not generic lead gen tools.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Real-Time Permit Feed</h3>
      <p>Ingests NYC DOB filings within minutes of submission. Filter by trade, borough, estimated value, and filing type.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🗺️</div>
      <h3>Interactive Trade Map</h3>
      <p>Visualize permit density across all five boroughs. Spot hot zones before your competitors and plan your outreach geographically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
      <h3>Instant Alerts</h3>
      <p>Get notified the moment a matching permit drops — via email, SMS, or push. Customize alert thresholds by job value and urgency.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Lead Pipeline CRM</h3>
      <p>Save, tag, and track permit leads through your sales process. Add notes, set follow-up reminders, and never drop a hot lead again.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
      <h3>Owner Contact Data</h3>
      <p>Access verified property owner details — phone, email, and mailing address — directly from the permit filing record.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
      <h3>Market Reports</h3>
      <p>Weekly and monthly reports showing permit volume trends, average job values, and competitive density by trade and borough.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

